title: Planet Of The Apes 1968 with greek subs.avi
description:
Planet Of The Apes 1968 with greek subs

O PLANHTHS TON PITHIKON 1968 ME ELLINIKOYS YPOTITLOYS


Enas astronayths ftanei se enan agnosto planhth kai katalhgei kynhghmenos  fylakismenos kai tapeinomenos, san ena zoo poy  to exmalotizoyn se ena kloybi.Gia toys katoikoys aytou toy planhth,enas anthropos einai akrivos ayto,ena zoo,ena  eidos katoterhs nohmosynhs.O logos gia toys pithikoys,to kyriarxo eidos se enan planhth opoy oi roloi exoyn apolytos antistrafei


Director: Franklin J. Schaffner
Writers: Michael Wilson (screenplay), Rod Serling (screenplay)
Stars: Charlton Heston, Roddy McDowall, Kim Hunter |
